title: Antiikkieno
overview: Oswald is an antique dealer with life on the line. My sister Emma suddenly pops into the shop to beg for a place to stay. Oswald promises accommodation for two nights. Creta's sister's tantrum changes Emma's overnight stay permanently, as Oswald-eno will do anything to make her sister's anger grow. A colorful coexistence begins, both at home and in the store.
